cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is about training convolutional neural network models, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS). Given that the paper focuses on memory efficiency, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG, followed by cs.CV and cs.NE. The use of approximations and the optimization of memory usage could also potentially place the paper under cs.AI and cs.DS.
